{"tid":665901,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"大灣區記者，打得！","createTime":"2018-05-15T11:25:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-15T14:49:14.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c5c168c1955bd9b641e52537fb88806f26164d9f","tid":665901,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T11:25:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/陳也/daily/article/20180515/20390771\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180515%2F20390771&d=cppOGrXEjPmccJsJqcfD7gRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=1f944d10\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180515%2F20390771&h=fec7f9fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/陳也/daily/article/20180515/20390771</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大灣區記者，打得！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20180515/large/1526285729_6a04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20180515%2Flarge%2F1526285729_6a04.jpg&h=a7874b24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n互聯網<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n香港記者在都江堰被打，瞬間又被兩個打手找上門，當面鞠躬道歉，恭稱記者為「老師」，打完閃速認錯，兒戲過九流電視劇。<br />\n點解打人？兩個平頭男，語言不詳，面目可疑。四川sorry sir得無厘頭。川式「被道歉」，無諗多咗，絕非內地新常態，只係咁啱好打得（尷尬啊）的林鄭到訪，汶川政府縱容毆打記者，太過落面，係嘛。<br />\n<br />\n記者這一次，看似扳回一仗，沒有白捱打。但都江堰難屬的災劫，被打手鎮壓，被當局屏蔽，被習帝做頭條的控災官腔洗板洗腦，難屬追討官員失職失責而惹毛官方的報復行動，肯定十年又十年，沒有伸張的渠道，只能遇到難得一見的香港記者時，強烈傾訴，請記者如實報道。<br />\n<br />\n都江堰聚源小學倒塌時死了二百個學生，十年過去，連申訴機會都要被「打走」，怪不得家屬情緒激動，拉住記者，不讓政府人員送走。有線記者和商台記者，是在家屬包圍（等同人肉保護）之下，才免於重蹈被李文足家園外的不知名人士飛踹踢翻！搶手機摔爛的極端超現實暴力對待！<br />\n<br />\n當N年後香港人成為必須向習帝感恩的大灣區人時，大灣區記者這個招牌，頂得住內地粗暴的拳腳？你信嗎？  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陳也 <br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"62dcca51ea8cebf864d2c775175ea1e07ce91dc5","tid":665901,"uid":183030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T14:30:31.000Z","msg":"到時就會有人話：打得好<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95fb33d547543c62111fb5e59e6d7bb964741899","tid":665901,"uid":183030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62dcca51ea8cebf864d2c775175ea1e07ce91dc5","tid":665901,"uid":183030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T14:30:31.000Z","msg":"到時就會有人話：打得好<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T14:31:02.000Z","msg":"依家都可能有.........<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c68ab914af5566b1de0d08134f0499f8c8e91e6","tid":665901,"uid":22913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T14:49:14.000Z","msg":"四川關我撚事咩 關心香港仲好啦"}]}